flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B{Install list ready?}
    B -- No --> C[Request list from engineer]
    B -- Yes --> D[Show summary: count, size, risks]
    D --> E{Blocked/critical items?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Require override or remove items]
    E -- No --> G{Approve batch install?}
    F --> G
    G -- No --> H[Cancel; return for revisions]
    G -- Yes --> I[Trigger batch install]
    I --> J{All items completed?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Notify success; record change set]
    J -- No --> L[Partial/failed; assign follow-up]
    K --> M([Done])
    L --> M

